    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, having been maintained with meticulous attention to detail and stored in a climate-controlled environment. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior upholstery, reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the secondary market. Mechanical integrity is absolute, verified by a comprehensive multi-point inspection. This is a premier opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that transcends the standard definitions of excellence.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
